Title: SocketIO4WinRT.Client
Description: This is a port of the SocketIO4Net.Client project, to run on WinRT (Windows 8) for C# users.
HomeWiki:
SocketIO4WinRT is a SocketIO client for WinRT (Windows 8 Mobile) C# clients. It is a port of SocketIO4Net.

For support, please create a discussion on the Discussions tab.

-- Chris Bordeman
